data.description: Sitting on the top of 5.66 acres, this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick ranch offers serene country living with a stocked trout stream running through the backyard. Enjoy stunning views from the living room's large windows overlooking the tranquil creek. The property features a spacious 2-story garage, perfect for storage or workshop space. Recent upgrades include a newer furnace, central air system, and hot water tank, ensuring comfort and efficiency year-round. The basement boasts a generous bonus room ideal for entertainment or relaxation, along with a convenient laundry area, gym space, and utility room. Whether you're unwinding by the creek, exploring the expansive grounds, or enjoying the modern amenities indoors, this property offers a peaceful retreat for nature lovers and outdoor enthusiasts alike.
